    "The Test Facility is accredited by the CCAC and AAALAC.",
    "Per the CCAC guidelines, this study was considered as a category of invasiveness C.",
    "The rhesus macaque study (n = 2) was conducted at the NIH Nonhuman Primate Testing Center for Evaluation of Somatic Cell Genome Editing Tools at the University of California, Davis (UC Davis).",
